item.title: CVE-2022-34443|2024-08-03T09:15:15.041Z -- dell -- rugged%20control%20center%20%28rcc%29
item.description: Dell Rugged Control Center, versions prior to 4.5, contain an Improper Input Validation in the Service EndPoint. A Local Low Privilege attacker could potentially exploit this vulnerability, leading to an Escalation of privileges.
